<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UNP-RECIBOS-APP</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://bootswatch.com/5/lux/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- CSS only -->
    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-pprn3073KE6tl6bjs2QrFaJGz5/SUsLqktiwsUTF55Jfv3qYSDhgCecCxMW52nD2" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar.ejs'); %>  
    <h2 class="text-center mt-5">RESETEAR</h2>  	
    <div class="w-50 mx-auto d-flex justify-content-center">
        <form action="resetear/?_method=DELETE" method="POST" id="formReset"></form>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-danger" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal">
            RESETEAR    
        </button>
    </div> 

    
      
      <!-- Modal -->
      <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">RESETEAR</h5>
              <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              Si resetea eliminara todos los datos cargados hasta el momento. ¿Esta seguro que quiere llevar acabo esta acción?
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">cerrar</button>
              <button class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm" type="submit" form="formReset">RESETEAR</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div> 
</body>
</html>